      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.FixedWidth.Exceptions.FieldConversionException",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.FixedWidth.Exceptions.FieldConversionException.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">The exception thrown when a field's raw string value cannot be converted to the\ntarget property type during a fixed-width read (extract) operation. Derives from\n<xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.FixedWidth.Exceptions.MalformedLineException\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
