      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.FixedWidth.Exceptions.FieldOverflowException",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.FixedWidth.Exceptions.FieldOverflowException.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">The exception thrown when a value converter or header converter returns a string\nthat is wider than the field width defined by\n<xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.FixedWidth.Attributes.FixedWidthFieldAttribute.Length\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>. This indicates a\nprogramming error — the converter does not respect the\n<xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.FixedWidth.FieldContext.FieldLength\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> contract.</p>\n"
    },
